They said we couldn't win NFC East....We did

They said without Jason Peters our offense would collapse...It didn't

They said Jay Ajayi wouldn't work out in Philly....Then they watched him play

They said we couldn't contend with the Cowboys....We embarrassed them at Jerry's World

They said our season was over without Carson Wentz....Well we weren't done

They said we couldn't make the playoffs....We did
